9. Qxb7 $2 gxh4 10. Qxa8 Qb6 $19) 9... Qb6 10. e3 Nbd7 $15) 8... Nbd7 9. Bd3
Bxd3 10. Qxd3 Bd6 11. O-O-O ({White demonstrates aggressive intentions rather
