least equality after} 14. Bd2 Ne5) 14... Ne5 15. Nxd4 Nxd3 16. Qxd3 Re5 $11)
9... dxe4 10. Nxe4 (10. Bxe4 e5 $132) 10... Nxe4 11. Bxe4 e5 {Yet another
branch of the Meran has occurred on the board with a2-a3 and Rf8-e8 included.
