c5 Bc7) 12... f6 13. Be3 (13. Bh4 exd4 14. Qd3 Nf8 $132) 13... exd4 14. Qxd4
Bc7 15. Rad1 $140 Qe7 $11 {proves that he is fine}) (6. cxd5 {cannot impress
