long the main line.}) 11. Nxe4 Nxe4 12. Bxe4 h6 13. Be3 (13. Rd1 {is the major
alternative, with a new choice after} exd4 {, as follows:} 14. Rxd4 (14. Nxd4
Nf6 15. Bf3 Re8 ({or} 15... Qa5 {at once}) 16. Nf5 Qa5 {[%cal Ge8e1]} 17. Ne3
Qe5 18. g3 Bf8 $11) 14... Qe7 15. Bxh6 (15. b3 Nf6 16. Bb2 Nxe4 (16... Re8 $11)
17. Rxe4 Qc7 18. Rc4 Qa5 {(very often this square is the best one for the queen
)} 19. Bc3 Qh5 20. Qd2 Be7 $11) (15. Bd2 Nf6 16. Bf5 (16. Re1 Nxe4 17. Rdxe4 (
17. Rexe4 Qc7) 17... Qd8 $11) 16... Qc7 17. Bc3 {This bishop has arrived at
