alternative is} 14. Bxd4 Nf6 {and now:} 15. Rfe1 (15. Bf5 Qa5 16. Bxc8 (16. Nh4
Be5 $11) 16... Rfxc8 17. Qb3 Qd5 18. Rfd1 (18. Bxf6 Qxb3 19. axb3 gxf6 $11) (
18. Qxd5 Nxd5 19. Rfd1 Rd8 20. Kf1 Nb4 21. Bc3 Nc6 $11 {and the few remaining
