(20. Re5 Qc7) 20... Kg8 21. Qc2 Qb5 22. Rad1 Rac8 $11) (19. a3 Re8 20. b4 Qb5
21. Re1 Kg8 22. Qb3 a6 23. Rad1 Rad8 $11) 19... Qxe1 20. Rfxe1 Nd5 (20... Rc7
21. Rad1 {, as in Malaniuk - Sharapov, Lazy, 2009, Black could improve his
