Bxf6 Qxb3 20. Bxg7+ (20. axb3 gxf6 21. Rfd1 Rd8 $11) 20... Kxg7 21. axb3 {
has won a pawn, but the subtle bishop transfer to the big diagonal} Be7 $44 {
[%cal Ge7f6]} 22. Rfe1 (22. Nd4 Bf6 23. Rfd1 Rc5) 22... Bf6 23. Re2 {and the
rook lift} Rc6 24. g3 Rb6 $11 {have left the enemy rooks stuck to protecting
