is a probable improvement, as shown by} 16. Qc2 O-O 17. Bxc4 Rc8 18. Nd6 Nxd6
19. exd6 Qxd6 $1 20. Rxb7 $140 Qc6 21. Re7 Qd6 22. Rxf7 Qb4+ 23. Nd2 Rxc4 24.
Rxg7+ Kxg7 25. Qxc4 Qxc4 26. Nxc4 Nc6 {and, quite typically, a long forced
